title: The List with Colleen Lopez 08.17.2017 - 10 PM
description:
The Fashion Edit has kicked off and we're bringing you the lastest for fall. Fall essentials from Lucky Brand, LaBellum by Hillary Scott, Naturalizer, and more! Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.
Prices shown on the previously recorded video may not represent the current price. Visit http://www.hsn.com to view the current selling price.
